OL,3,CActivity centre backs bid for
OL,4,Cchildren's right to week of outdoor
OL,5,Ceducation
OL,7,FA move to make it law to give every
OL,8,Fpupil in Scotland the right to a week
OL,9,Fof residential outdoor education has
OL,10,Fbeen welcomed by a Borders activity
OL,11,Fcentre.
OL,13,FThe member's Bill from Scottish
OL,14,FConservative MSP Liz Smith was backed
OL,15,Fby Holyrood earlier this year.
OL,17,FIt would have fallen if the Scottish
OL,18,FGovernment had not brought forward a
OL,19,Ffinancial report - known as a
OL,20,Ffinancial resolution - by the end of
OL,21,Fthis week.
