OL,7,FThe Children's Minister Natalie Don-
OL,8,FInnes had raised concerns about the
OL,9,Faffordability of the bill, which the
OL,10,FEducation Committee estimated could
OL,11,Fcost up to #40 million.
OL,13,FThat led to criticism that she was
OL,14,Fblocking the will of parliament, and
OL,15,Fon Wednesday she backtracked,
OL,16,Fconfirming to MSPs that the necessary
OL,17,Fpapers had been lodged.
OL,19,FStaff at Whithaugh, an activity centre
OL,20,Frun by Rock UK in Newcastleton,
OL,21,Fwelcomed the news.
