OL,5,Ceducation
OL,7,FSenior Instructor Sarah King said "I
OL,8,Fthink it's incredibly important to
OL,9,Fsupport this bill and to be able to
OL,10,Fget our kids outdoors"
OL,12,F"It an show them there are different
OL,13,Fways of learning and there's different
OL,14,Fpaths they can take.
OL,16,F"That can open up new hobbies which
OL,17,Fcan increase a massive amount of
OL,18,Fconfidence in a child's day-today
OL,19,Flife."
