OL,5,Ceducation
OL,7,FThe bill will now be considered by
OL,8,Fcommittees at the Scottish Parliament,
OL,9,Fand could be amended before a final
OL,10,Fvote on whether it becomes law.
OL,12,FIf it is passed, it would mean all
OL,13,Fschool pupils in Scotland are entitled
OL,14,Fto five days and four nights of
OL,15,Foutdoor learning at a residential
OL,16,Fcentre.
