OL,7,FWhithaugh Centre Manager Ben Fortescue
OL,8,Fsaid it was "fantastic" that the bill
OL,9,Fnow had the financial backing to
OL,10,Fproceed, and the new law could benefit
OL,11,Fpupils as well as the outdoor activity
OL,12,Fsector.
OL,14,FA similar law, which would apply to
OL,15,FEngland, Wales and Northern Ireland,
OL,16,Fhas been tabled at Westminster by
OL,17,FLiberal Democrat MP Tim Farron.
